  EventText: "Passing by a Gorgon\u2019s layer, a certain statue catches your eye.
    A young man lies on his back, one hand held up in either awe or self defense.
    His eyes are almost squeezed shut, but one is just barely peeking."
  BackgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: a3c52912f93e47a44aa7ee941841e337, type: 3}
